{
  "stem": "4226.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in-- that was-- 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I, I was born in '26, and the war broke out in 1940.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The war with Russia broke out '41.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So with France, that was a quick-- a quick work over, [LAUGHS] practically.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, we met groups of-- not in my village, but in Oradea, where, where I went to high school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could remember on Fridays, they used to have transports coming from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They-- one of the large bakeries used to bake extra bread and bring them out to the station.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was Jewish people who went to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 173,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Traveling on trains going towards the Black Sea Port.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of them, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them spoke Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were Austrian Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the Black Sea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they, they had passports.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and some had, of course, entry permits, British entry permits to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 178,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it must have been '42-- '41, '42.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was in a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And other schools had a very-- in the same town, we had about six high schools, mixed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some were co-educational, and some weren't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some were Romanian language.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some were-- had Hungarian language.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And many Jewish people had two schools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they went to those two schools as--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One, one was an Orthodox high school, and one was Reformist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 181,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had a choice of two schools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Four, four boys' schools.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they had separate girls' schools, as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 183,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were very many schools.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 183,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some were state schools.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 183,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some were-- belonged to different churches.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 184,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 185,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 186,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not so much of Europe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 186,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only when the Germans entered Hungary, things changed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 187,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was effects in the war, because we had-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] anti-Semitism was growing, and--",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
